values:
October is here! <3

Means I get to go out and embrace the sweet grace of the candy!

And also hang out more with my friends so boo-ya. In other news, I have been watching the pandas and I absolutly love them, Tai Shan is so small and cute, his such a fuzzball [fangirl scream]. 

Weather: Cold, breezy, Sunny,

And cause of the weather I now got a new scarf! Hehe its soft and fwuffy. I very much enjoy it, and it keeps me warm surprisingly. And with the winter coming in. I am working on my lain bear hat...mother got me the stuff to make it.

Charlie my pet duck is missing, i came back from work tired, I feel like shit and I am worried for charlie. I serched everywhere and now I'm scared that he will end up dead like his brother,not sure what to do anymore, I hope dad finds him soon.

I sent dad off to find him, cause 1st I don't want to find him dead like his brother and 2nd its dark, I'm should not be out in the dark. charlie meh duckie come back to me! ;-;

I'm lost without you! I thought what we had was special why charlie did you live, I loved you! x.x ( I feel so bad....)

x.X -dead-

Getting new glasses today, that shell rock my socks! I had been begging for some new ones and now I get them, thank you, thank you! In other news I shall try making a pair of Chi's ears from chobits and go crazy with them.:3

Getting a digital camra soon, and going to be a picture whore so beat that! X3Also needing new pencils and crap, cause my pencils are like doomed to last for only a couple more days and I need to draw, else I turn to a zombie.

Need to go to the doctors, need to buy some clothes, hats, hats shoes, more hats, candy and icecream! x)

Big sweet tooth person here, love candy and sweets <3 yum yum yum!
